channel.title: Where is the 508cache?
channel.description: Hey I was bored so I though why not test out a 508 or something..I read some tutorials and I needed to move the 508cache to the .titana cache 32. For some reason I cannot find the 508 cache in my C:/WINDOWS. I have my titana cache all installed and everything just can't find that 508cache..

item.title: Where is the 508cache?
